# Environment Variables for Mobile App

## Required Variables

### API Configuration
API_URL=http://10.0.2.2:5000/api

## Notes

- For Android Emulator, use http://10.0.2.2:5000/api
- For iOS Simulator, use http://localhost:5000/api
- For physical devices, use your computer's IP address (e.g., http://192.168.1.100:5000/api)
- For production, use your deployed API URL (e.g., https://api.mycircle.com/api)

## Google OAuth Configuration

Google OAuth is configured in the app.json file:
- Web Client ID is used for authentication
- Android/iOS Client IDs are configured in Google Cloud Console
- Redirect URIs are automatically handled by Expo

Never commit the actual .env file to version control
